1
00:00:04,110 --> 00:00:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moegi-san?</font>

2
00:00:07,660 --> 00:00:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, join the other team.</font>

3
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

4
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But?</font>

5
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what?</font>

6
00:00:17,190 --> 00:00:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing. Right?</font>

7
00:00:22,030 --> 00:00:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry.</font>

8
00:01:01,370 --> 00:01:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no one here.</font>

9
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

10
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

11
00:01:24,940 --> 00:01:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kozue, look at this...</font>

12
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kozue?</font>

13
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishida-san?</font>

14
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

15
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're there, aren't you?</font>

16
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. This isn't funny.</font>

17
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are they screwing around?</font>

18
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're interrogating her.</font>

19
00:02:16,090 --> 00:02:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

20
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Where are you hiding the weapons?</font>

21
00:02:18,410 --> 00:02:22,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were ordered not to use violence.</font>

22
00:02:20,370 --> 00:02:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I really don't know.</font>

23
00:02:23,610 --> 00:02:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Breaking fingers would be faster.</font>

24
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Really? Tickle, tickle!</font>

25
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, that's not a good 
idea with this many players.</font>

26
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

27
00:02:33,580 --> 00:02:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The breakdown of morals 
makes groups fall apart.</font>

28
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:41,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My job is to chaperone the new players.</font>

29
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

30
00:02:44,790 --> 00:02:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name is Kushieda.</font>

31
00:02:46,730 --> 00:02:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are about thirty people on her team.</font>

32
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of them are new, and someone 
named Moegi is ruling by fear.</font>

33
00:02:54,490 --> 00:02:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we might be the better group.</font>

34
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

35
00:03:02,410 --> 00:03:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tickle, tickle, tickle!</font>

36
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just looks like kids playing to me.</font>

37
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's surprisingly effective.</font>

38
00:03:13,550 --> 00:03:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever been tickled 
by that many people?</font>

39
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:19,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, no.</font>

40
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tickle, tickle!</font>

41
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

42
00:03:26,490 --> 00:03:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sumiyaka-san, what are you doing?</font>

43
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. This does seem effective.</font>

44
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice try.</font>

45
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't... You jerk...</font>

46
00:03:55,810 --> 00:03:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh.</font>

47
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sumiyaka-san.</font>

48
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:18,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My next game is my thirtieth.</font>

49
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You believe in that curse?</font>

50
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize you were cute like that.</font>

51
00:04:41,370 --> 00:04:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me hold you for a while.</font>

52
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

53
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn!</font>

54
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for that.</font>

55
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're teammates, after all.</font>

56
00:06:59,670 --> 00:07:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, but thanks anyway.</font>

57
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

58
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

59
00:07:23,010 --> 00:07:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

60
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, could you cut that out?</font>

61
00:07:25,650 --> 00:07:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

62
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

63
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you hear me? Enough already!</font>

64
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

65
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not what you think! 
All of our teammates were killed, so I...</font>

66
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't have a choice.</font>

67
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't run away! I didn't—</font>

68
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

69
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

70
00:07:56,380 --> 00:08:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. I just ran away, too.</font>

71
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

72
00:08:01,710 --> 00:08:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ran? What do you mean by that?</font>

73
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

74
00:08:05,660 --> 00:08:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

75
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hurt?</font>

76
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

77
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. Are you cold?</font>

78
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

79
00:08:14,770 --> 00:08:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many are still alive?</font>

80
00:08:16,530 --> 00:08:19,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

81
00:08:19,710 --> 00:08:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

82
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

83
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

84
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going to happen to us?</font>

85
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

86
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The tutorial has concluded.</i></font>

87
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please figure the rest out yourselves.</i></font>

88
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tutorial has concluded.</font>

89
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please figure the rest out yourselves.</font>

90
00:09:10,690 --> 00:09:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The grey nightjar is a truly hideous bird.</font>

91
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its face is spotted like it has 
flecks of miso all over it.</font>

92
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for waiting.</font>

93
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were amazing.</font>

94
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You killed so many so freely.</font>

95
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please make me your student!</font>

96
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you like animals?</font>

97
00:10:27,780 --> 00:10:29,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like dogs and cats.</font>

98
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't dislike them.</font>

99
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think of 
people who keep pets?</font>

100
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't like their sense of superiority.</font>

101
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if a child were 
being loud on the bus?</font>

102
00:11:00,810 --> 00:11:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd think they were annoying.</font>

103
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are your parents alive?</font>

104
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

105
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you love them?</font>

106
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to kill them.</font>

107
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really?</font>

108
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:48,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ask Shion if you have any questions.</font>

109
00:11:48,190 --> 00:11:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

110
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion-san.</font>

111
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'm Moegi. Nice to meet you.</font>

112
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know what's making that sound?</font>

113
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

114
00:13:54,930 --> 00:13:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your clothes are cute, Kyara-san.</font>

115
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they?</font>

116
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a lot of loose clothes.</font>

117
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

118
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you'd look good in 
form-fitting clothes, too.</font>

119
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike me, you're pretty.</font>

120
00:14:13,300 --> 00:14:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't like constricting clothing.</font>

121
00:14:19,770 --> 00:14:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'm sorry.</font>

122
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

123
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to kill someone 
after this. Care to join me?</font>

124
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

125
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

126
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll drive there.</font>

127
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll teach you how to kill.</font>

128
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"'The king decreed that we're allowed 
to stop playing on cloudy days,</font>

129
00:15:20,370 --> 00:15:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we were playing the flute 
because it's just so fun.'"</font>

130
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Pose briefly stopped playing to speak."</font>

131
00:15:30,210 --> 00:15:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"'But he'd never let us travel.</font>

132
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The clouds could clear at any time.'"</font>

133
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The comet said,</font>

134
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Don't worry. The king told me so 
himself the other day.</font>

135
00:15:50,890 --> 00:15:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said to let those twins 
travel one cloudy night.</font>

136
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go. Let's go.</font>

137
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm lots of fun.</font>

138
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My nickname is the whale of the sky.</font>

139
00:16:12,780 --> 00:16:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know that?</font>

140
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All those frail stars like sardines</font>

141
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and black rocks like killifish...</font>

142
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gobble them all up.'"</font>

143
00:17:32,540 --> 00:17:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you kill your parents?</font>

144
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet.</font>

145
00:17:44,970 --> 00:17:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

146
00:17:55,870 --> 00:17:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are good, aren't they?</font>

147
00:18:02,060 --> 00:18:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The fern frond drank the morning mist 
and swayed green and cold.</font>

148
00:18:11,910 --> 00:18:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The grey nightjar squeaked high and loud.</font>

149
00:18:18,590 --> 00:18:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it tidied up its nest,</font>

150
00:18:22,670 --> 00:18:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">fixed its feathers and down,</font>

151
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and flew out of the nest again."</font>

152
00:18:34,970 --> 00:18:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The mist cleared,</font>

153
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the sun was rising in the east.</font>

154
00:18:43,490 --> 00:18:48,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The grey nightjar endured 
the dizzyingly bright light</font>

155
00:18:49,350 --> 00:18:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and flew toward it like an arrow."</font>

156
00:18:57,360 --> 00:19:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"'Sun. Oh, sun.</font>

157
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:08,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please take me to your place.</font>

158
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care if I burn to death.</font>

159
00:19:14,430 --> 00:19:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even my ugly body</font>

160
00:19:19,590 --> 00:19:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will produce a small light 
when it's burned.'"</font>

161
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The fern frond drank the morning mist</font>

162
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and swayed green and cold.</font>

163
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:07,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The grey nightjar... 
The grey nightjar..."</font>

164
00:22:13,010 --> 00:22:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sun. Oh, sun.</i></font>

165
00:22:18,710 --> 00:22:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please take me with you.</i></font>

166
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please turn a weakling like me</i></font>

167
00:22:28,130 --> 00:22:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>into someone as strong as you.</i></font>

168
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moegi-san.</font>

169
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One of the girls said 
she saw something strange.</font>

170
00:22:42,930 --> 00:22:46,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There was a naked and dead stump.</font>

171
00:22:46,850 --> 00:22:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The body was really badly damaged.</font>

172
00:22:50,610 --> 00:22:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki.</font>

173
00:22:52,130 --> 00:22:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you see the girl with 
long caramel-colored hair?</font>

174
00:22:55,770 --> 00:22:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there a problem?</font>

175
00:22:57,650 --> 00:23:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't find her anywhere. 
She's apparently—</font>

176
00:23:00,590 --> 00:23:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone!</font>

177
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone stand up!</font>

178
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... But then there 
won't be enough for us...</font>

179
00:23:10,710 --> 00:23:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moegi-san?</font>

180
00:23:12,490 --> 00:23:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I don't know what to do.</font>

181
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run! The plan's on hold!</font>

182
00:23:18,080 --> 00:23:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her killing is like drinking seawater.</font>

183
00:23:21,930 --> 00:23:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once she starts, she doesn't stop.</font>

184
